{
  "stem": "4710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And parallel, we learned specific Jewish studies as I got grown older.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By the age of 13, I believe, I-- I started studying in yeshiva full time, which was in our town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only-- only Jewish subject, I mean Talmud.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the school went up to 14, but somehow I left at 13, because-- because the last class, there was not enough people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of the children went to a-- went to gymnasium, so there was not enough left, enough children left in the elementary school to have the last-- the  14-year-olds.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I left the school completely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I really had education up to the-- up to the age of 13.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They called it just [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Hungarian Autonomic Orthodox State School.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think-- I think that defines the Orthodox community which had an autonomic existence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as far as the subject, we had to-- there was a prescribed by the minister of education what to learn about the general subject-- general secular subject, thrown in a bit of Jewish subjects.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to celebrate, the school, all the national Hungarian holidays, like the 15th of March, when we had to wear something-- colored ribbons.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the Independence Day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And always have the greatest respect to our great leader Horthy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even the rabbi came to the school to-- to make a sermon about-- about how significant day it is, the Hungarian independence.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I realized that by that time, this is something-- nothing to be proud of, of being-- being Hungarian, and we are not really Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But-- but you had to pretend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were-- we were trying at that time to show to the non-Jewish people that we are-- we are as good Hungarians as they are.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
